  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Continental "breakfast box" delievered daily to your room, for you to enjoy a relaxing breakfast in your own time, either in your room or on the balcony with a view.</li>
<li>Breakfast boxes include fresh crossaints, bread rolls, yoghurt, orange juice and cereals, whilst you will find milk, butter and jam already in the fridge.</li>
<li>Half board evening meals are taken in adjacent villa Orselina and are 3 courses with choice of menu.</li>
<li>Bed and Breakfast reduction also available.</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
