  <description><![CDATA[<p>With stunning views over Locarno and Lake Maggiore from its quiet location just 2 minutes’ walk from the top of the Madonna del Sasso funicular, we are pleased to introduce this tastefully-furnished hotel to our programme for Summer 2015. The funicular takes guests to Locarno centre in 10 minutes allowing guests to enjoy this bustling city from a peaceful, idyllic spot above the city. La Barca Blu’s sister hotel, the adjacent Villa Orselina (5 star), is where the half board evening meals are served and guests can also use its fantastic spa and wellness facilities at a discounted rate.</p>]]></description>
